                            "aonid": 108
                        }
                    ],
                    "effect": "The  *spider lily tattoo* manipulates your life force to make you appear to be undead for a short time. Attempt a Deception check against the triggering undead creature's Perception DC. On a success, the triggering undead believes you're undead as well\u2014a mindless undead is likely to ignore you, while a sapient undead might react with curiosity or confusion. You can continue attempting Deception checks each round as a single action to Sustain the effect for up to 1 minute.",
